text.data-name: Utilization gains directly impacting improvement in Gross Margins ranging from 4%-15%
PS supply management and continued increased client delivery performance (WFH efficiency) drive improvements in utilization
Reduction in non billable cost and also discretionary cost not related to demand is helping the margin. Beach is building up and exchange rate is also putting pressure in GP.
2H’22 utilization/GM dip expected to be managed through demand/supply alignment. Hire only unstaffed ATL role.
